2026-05-14T05:47:24.0045423Z 223        <!--
2026-05-14T05:47:24.0046206Z 224            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-14T05:47:24.0047348Z 225            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-14T05:47:24.0048614Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-14T05:47:24.0049690Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-14T05:47:24.0050643Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
